# The release bundle is published as a GitHub release ASSET (via `gh release`), not tracked
# here — it duplicates the asset and the ~194 MB git blob made `git push` hang. It is built
# locally (MCP assemble_release) and uploaded as the release download.
dmxsmartlink.zip

# The Windows installer is staged into dist_windows/ for the release-zip build AND published as
# a standalone release asset. It exceeds GitHub's 100 MB in-repo limit — never commit it.
dist_windows/DMXSmartLink-Setup.exe
dist_windows/*.exe

# The macOS installer is staged into dist_macos/ for the release-zip build AND published as a
# standalone release asset. It exceeds GitHub's 100 MB in-repo limit — never commit it.
dist_macos/DMXSmartLink-Installer.pkg
dist_macos/*.pkg

# Local scratch
*.tmp
__pycache__/
